OL,3,CYorkshire Water hosepipe ban to
OL,4,Ccontinue despite expected heavy rain
OL,6,FYorkshire Water says a hosepipe ban
OL,7,Fwill remain in place despite forecasts
OL,8,Fof heavy rain.
OL,10,FRestrictions on the use of hosepipes
OL,11,Fhave been in place since 11 July,
OL,12,Ffollowing a long period of dry weather
OL,13,Fand decreasing reservoir levels.
OL,15,FYorkshire Water said the county
OL,16,Fexperienced the driest spring in 132
OL,17,Fyears.
OL,19,FAugust is expected to be the seventh
OL,20,Fmonth in a row of below average
OL,21,Frainfall.
