OL,3,CYorkshire Water hosepipe ban to
OL,4,Ccontinue despite expected heavy rain
OL,6,FYorkshire's reservoir stocks currently
OL,7,Fstand at 35.8% - less than half the
OL,8,Fexpected levels for the time of year.
OL,10,FGroundwater stocks in East Yorkshire
OL,11,Fare also being impacted by the
OL,12,Fprolonged dry weather.
OL,14,FDave Kaye, director of water at
OL,15,FYorkshire Water, said: "We're
OL,16,Fexpecting some more welcome rainfall
OL,17,Fover the next few days. While welcome,
OL,18,Fit is likely to be taken up by plants
OL,19,Fand the parched ground and
OL,20,Fcountryside, with very little making
OL,21,Fits way into our reservoirs.
