OL,3,CYorkshire Water hosepipe ban to
OL,4,Ccontinue despite expected heavy rain
OL,6,F"Hosepipe restrictions will remain in
OL,7,Fplace until reservoir stocks have
OL,8,Frecovered. This could extend into the
OL,9,Fwinter as we are planning for the
OL,10,Fshort-term and to ensure we have
OL,11,Fadequate supplies heading into the
OL,12,Fspring and summer of 2026.
OL,14,F"The efforts of customers to reduce
OL,15,Fwater usage, our work to reduce
OL,16,Fleakage and the drought orders and
OL,17,Fpermits we have in place, as well as
OL,18,Fothers we have applied for, are all
OL,19,Fhelping to reduce demand and protect
OL,20,Fthe water stocks so everyone will have
OL,21,Fthe water they need."
