OL,4,Ccontinue despite expected heavy rain
OL,6,FThe restrictions ban the use of
OL,7,Fhosepipes to water gardens, wash cars
OL,8,For carry out any other domestic
OL,9,Factivities.
OL,11,FThere are exemptions for some
OL,12,Fcustomers and businesses.
OL,14,FCustomers who ignore the ban could
OL,15,Fface fines of up to #1,000.
